{"tid":2495566,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"滙控取消倫敦總部高層樓層 祈耀年改非固定座位","createTime":"2021-04-19T09:07:15.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-19T09:20:40.000Z","uid":73092,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"be6dca69d1fd33f9655b1b714252f9dc95141f70","tid":2495566,"uid":73092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T09:07:15.000Z","msg":"滙豐控股(00005)取消位於倫敦金絲雀碼頭總部的高級職員的樓層，滙控行政總裁祈耀年(Noel Quinn)及其他高層人員的42樓辦公室，將會改建為客戶會議室及協作空間。<br />\n<br />\n祈耀年對英國《金融時報》稱，他及其他高級管理人員將不在42樓工作，並會在較下兩層的共享工作間以非固定工作枱工作，因高級職員均要到世界各地出差，他的辦公室有一半時間是空置，認為沒必要再擁有一間辦公室，這是一種新的辦公室趨勢。<br />\n<br />\n祈耀年又透露，滙控沒計劃續租大部分市中心未來3至5年期內到期的租約，而且亦實開始實行每兩名員工，共用一張辦公桌的政策。<br />\n<br />\n信報"},{"pid":"773755702583dadb99b928441dce5469a99bce75","tid":2495566,"uid":38904,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T09:11:24.000Z","msg":"即係區區有ceo office?<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12fd7df783bee1cfc65451fe769b4386718619a4","tid":2495566,"uid":78184,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T09:15:17.000Z","msg":"商廈需求大減"},{"pid":"af4dbe2e2c2e6546288013fd0df1df7a3aa9b360","tid":2495566,"uid":195248,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T09:15:52.000Z","msg":"HSBC都劏房文化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n執柒左去喇"},{"pid":"672a68a22d1925523c99ed17a182b26b96c5a5bd","tid":2495566,"uid":4564,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T09:17:19.000Z","msg":"每兩名員工，共用一張辦公桌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n倫敦金？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1f9d576bc3590977a78b5ab299a718dae70da9e","tid":24955